      "plain": "Features added\nWe coded the architecture to support modular plugins where each module supports a file extension. For example, we coded a focus writer mode.\nOther features\nRefactored files into workspaces and quickboards\nAdded support for portable boards with embedded files like pictures\nTools palette\nWorkspace home screen, start screen."
